the view's coordinate 
 the view is left down in positon. like below:
        ———————————
       |           |
       |           |
       |  (cx,cy)  |
       |           |  
       |___________|
   （x,y）
   cx = x + mxRadius;
   cy = y + myRadius;
   canvas.rotate((float)mRotate, cx, cy);
   
